column5: What's the problem Mikey, another skunk?.. maybe Mr. Mean Fishy took your tackle away from you again???  .. spit it out son!... we won't laugh... too much!!!

Was going to ask for opinions and reviews on a new book titled "The story of the lost fourm member GCD" but nobody bought it....   Na, seriously I wanted to get the Quantum PT Energy reel but it was sold out on Cabelas site.
There's only one reel worth it's salt... and it's name is Shimano!!!   ... always remember that!!!
What do you throw GCD, like what baitcast reels do u use?  Just curious
A Shimano reel is to fishing as Honda is to cars.
Heh, why am I not surprised the Dawg fishes Shimano reels spooled with Vanish.  Hell he probably drives a Ford too! Just couldn't pick a winner in a one horse race.   Actually more like Chrysler.
